<div class="inner" id="msg_921033">Staggering Reflexes (Ex): At 1st level, a waylayer gains a bonus on initiative checks equal to 1/2 her level (minimum +1) if she acts in a surprise round, and is never flat-footed at the start of combat (even if she fails to act during the surprise round). This ability replaces trapfinding.<br>waylayer这里应该是即使她不能在突袭论行动，她也不会陷入措手不及</div>
