<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1125993">海怪之主的自然变身：<br>A kraken caller’s options for wild shape are limited to animals with the <span style="color: blue;" class="bbc_color">aquatic</span> or <span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color">water subtype</span>&nbsp; or that have the <span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color">amphibious</span> special quality. <br>海怪之主只能变形为拥有<span style="color: blue;" class="bbc_color">水栖生物类别</span>、<span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color">水系亚种</span>或是<span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color">两栖</span>能力的动物。<br><br>&nbsp;<img src="/bbs/Smileys/converted/em032.gif" alt="&#58;em032" title="&#58;em032" border="0" class="smiley"/>顺带一提，根本没有水系亚种的动物<del>而有两栖的只有俩</del><br><div class="quoteheader"><div class="topslice_quote">引用</div></div><blockquote class="bbc_standard_quote">水系亚种 (Water Subtype)：此亚种一般是水元素位面相关的元素和异界生物。水系生物总是具有游泳速度，在水中移动时不需要进行游泳检定。水系生物可以在水下呼吸，通常也可以呼吸空气。水系亚种将游泳视为本职技能。</blockquote><div class="quotefooter"><div class="botslice_quote"></div></div></div>
</div>
</div>
